column1: 22 pcs Stainless Steel Needles for  in a Black Case (Color: Silver)
column21:
1. Please confirm that the instruments and accessories from tattoo shop are sterilized. 
   The tattoo artist should wear disposable gloves. 
   It is advisable to use the needles and machines which made of stainless steel. 
   2. Please note the quality of tattoo pigments. 
   Liquid plant pigments with alcohol are used in modern 
    instead of dye and ink, because it is extracted from natural plants and can reduce infections after penetration. 
   3. Self-protection: adrenaline are used to cleanse the skin and to stop bleeding in the process. 
   To reduce infection, you need to clean the skin with warm water and keep it dry for one week. 
   4. Use animal blood or vermilion 
   Mixture of pigeon blood and vermilion may endanger your life. 
   5. Do not use alcohol or gentian violet liquid to handle the wound (alcohol will irritate the wound and gentian violet liquid will ruin the tattoo image.). 
    package content: 22 x Needles
